<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>DriveApp - Your Cloud, Your Way</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      color: #333;
    }

    header {
      background-color: #1a73e8;
      color: white;
      padding: 16px 32px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    nav a {
      margin-left: 20px;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 80px 20px 60px;
      background-color: #e8f0fe;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 42px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #1a237e;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #444;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .cta {
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .btn, .btn-outline {
      padding: 12px 22px;
      font-size: 16px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 8px;
      display: inline-block;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .btn {
      background-color: #1a73e8;
      color: white;
      border: none;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #1662c4;
    }

    .btn-outline {
      background-color: transparent;
      border: 2px solid #1a73e8;
      color: #1a73e8;
    }

    .btn-outline:hover {
      background-color: #dce7ff;
    }

    .features {
      padding: 60px 20px;
      background-color: #fff;
    }

    .features h2 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      color: #1a237e;
    }

    .feature-grid {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 30px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .feature-box {
      background-color: #f9fbff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      padding: 24px;
      width: 260px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .feature-box h3 {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .feature-box p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #555;
    }

    footer {
      background-color: #111;
      color: #bbb;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero h1 {
        font-size: 32px;
      }

      .feature-box {
        width: 90%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div class="logo">üìÅ DriveApp</div>
    <nav>
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/user/register">Register</a>
      <a href="/user/login">Login</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Store. Access. Share.</h1>
    <p>Welcome to DriveApp ‚Äì your personal cloud for safely storing and sharing files from any device, anytime.</p>
    <div class="cta">
      <a href="/user/register" class="btn">Create Account</a>
      <a href="/user/login" class="btn-outline">Sign In</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <h2>What makes DriveApp awesome?</h2>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature-box">
        <h3>üì§ Easy Upload</h3>
        <p>Drag and drop your files or upload them in seconds with a clean, simple interface.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-box">
        <h3>üîê Fully Encrypted</h3>
        <p>Your files are stored securely using end-to-end encryption. Only you can access them.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-box">
        <h3>üîó Instant Sharing</h3>
        <p>Need to send a file? Share a secure link instantly without hassle or downloads.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
